Hybrid Journals: Venues Metadata

Source: R/data.R
jct_oalex_venues.Rd

This datasets contains information about journals. These journals come from the Journal Checker Tool.

Usage

jct_oalex_venues

Format

An object of class tbl_df (inherits from tbl, data.frame) with 12743 rows and 3 columns.

Examples

jct_oalex_venues
